				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The problem with using single screen mirroring for 8-way scroll is that you get garbage at the top and bottom as well as the sides. Using vertical mirroring for 8-way scroll (like SMB3 and Crystalis) removes the top/bottom garbage and still allows you to have a status bar.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

